    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "return items.map((item, i) => {\n\tconst meta = $('Limit').all()[i].json;\n\n\tlet keyword = 'viral content';\n\ttry { keyword = $('Edit Fields').first().json.keyword || keyword; } catch(e) {\n\t\ttry { keyword = $('Set Schedule Keyword').first().json.keyword || keyword; } catch(e2) {}\n\t}\n\n\tconst prompt = `Keyword/Niche: ${keyword}\nTikTok caption: ${meta.caption || '(no caption)'}\nCreator: @${meta.author || 'unknown'}\nViews: ${meta.views || 0}\nShares: ${meta.shares || 0}\nDuration: ${meta.duration || 0}s\n\nBased on this specific TikTok video about \"${keyword}\", create a UNIQUE Pinterest pin title and description. Reference the actual caption content and niche. Do NOT use generic phrases — make it specific to THIS video.`;\n\n\treturn {\n\t\tjson: {\n\t\t\t...meta,\n\t\t\tdrive_file_id: item.json.id,\n\t\t\tdrive_url: item.json.webViewLink,\n\t\t\tdrive_name: item.json.name,\n\t\t\tprompt: prompt\n\t\t}\n\t};\n});"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
